<%= render 'shared/title' %>
<div class="jumbotron">
  <%= image_tag "logo_white_239x50.png", class: "landing-page-logo" %>
  <span class="pull-right">
    <%= link_to "Sign in", new_user_session_path, class: "sign-in-label" %>
    <%= link_to "<i class='fa fa-rocket fa-2x white'></i>".html_safe,
                new_user_session_path,
                class: "sign-in-icon" %> 
  </span>
  <%= render 'shared/share_buttons' %>
  <br>
  <h1>
    Master Your Priorities
  </h1>
  <h2>Get updated, stay motivated and take action</h2>
  <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
    <blockquote>
      <p class="pull-right">
        <%= image_tag("Hemingway_portrait_120x120.jpg", size: "50x50", alt: "Never mistake motion for action.") %>
      </p>
      <h3>Never mistake motion for action.</h3>
      <br>
      <span class="pull-right"><small><cite>by Ernest Hemingway</cite></small></span>
    </blockquote>
  </div>
  <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
    <br><br>
    <%= link_to "Start Today", new_user_registration_path, { class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg centered", id: "sign-up" } %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container landing-page" id="learnmore">
  <br><br>
  <div class="row">
    <h2>What is Rakepage?</h2>
    <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
      <p class="landing-feature-text">
        For people who are distracted by wasting time online, Rakepage is a productivity tool to maximize your focus on your priorities. Build new habits to take action and keep motivated to get things done.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <br><br><hr><br><br><br>

  <div class="row">
    <h2>Maximize Your Focus</h2>
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <p class="landing-feature-text">
        If you commit to nothing, you’re distracted by everything.
      </p>
      <p class="landing-feature-text">
        Discover the power of less and master your priorities.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>Top 5 Topics</h3>
      <p class="landing-feature-text">
        <i class="fa fa-bullseye purple"></i>&nbsp;
        Commit to your most important topics.
      </p>
      <p class="landing-feature-text">
        <i class="fa fa-rocket purple"></i>&nbsp;
        Stop aimless browsing, be online with a purpose.
      </p>
      <div class="landing-screenshot-left">
        <%= image_tag("screenshot_choose_topic.jpg", class: "img-responsive") %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>Stay Focused</h3>
      <p class="landing-feature-text">
        <i class="fa fa-star purple"></i>&nbsp;
        News, bookmarks and tasks - all in one place.
      </p>
      <p class="landing-feature-text">
        <i class="fa fa-bolt purple"></i>&nbsp;
        Get updated, motivated and take action.
      </p>
      <div class="landing-screenshot">
        <%= image_tag("screenshot_news_bookmarks_tasks.jpg", class: "img-responsive") %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <br><br><hr><br><br><br>

  <div class="row">
    <h2>Build New Habits</h2>
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <p class="landing-feature-text">
        Motion is when you’re busy doing something, but that task will never produce an outcome by itself.
      </p>
      <p class="landing-feature-text">
        Action, on the other hand, is the type of behavior that will get you a result.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>Take Action</h3>
      <p class="landing-feature-text">
        <i class="fa fa-tasks purple"></i>&nbsp;
        Transform news and bookmarks to tasks.
      </p>
      <p class="landing-feature-text">
        <i class="fa fa-calendar purple"></i>&nbsp;
        Set a schedule for your actions.
      </p>
      <div class="landing-screenshot-left">
        <%= image_tag("screenshot_task.jpg", class: "img-responsive") %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <h3>Accountability</h3>
      <p class="landing-feature-text">
        <i class="fa fa-line-chart purple"></i>&nbsp;
        Track your productivity and stay motivated.
      </p>
      <p class="landing-feature-text">
        <i class="fa fa-flag-checkered purple"></i>&nbsp;
        Don't break your chain!
      </p>
      <div class="landing-screenshot">
        <%= image_tag("screenshot_chains.jpg", class: "img-responsive") %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br><br><hr><br>
  <br><br>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">
      <%= link_to "Get a preview", master_rakes_path, { class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg centered", id: "take-a-look" } %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br><br>
</div>

